data.title: Council Bluffs Transload Terminal
data.text:
Conveniently located near Omaha, Nebraska, the Council Bluffs Transload Terminal offers rail access to all Class I carriers and is located close to I-80 and I-29.

Warehousing/Material Handling

Accessible by rail and truck

Unload or load railcars and trucks

Transload breakbulk and bulk (dry and liquid) commodities

Outdoor storage

Terminal Features

15 railcar spots

Multiple conveyors

Multiple forklifts

Commodities

Specializing in bulk, breakbulk, and liquid commodities including:

Lumber

Steel

Shingles

Corn oil

Soda ash

Grain
